{"tid":1908773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍店360仲有得加租咁勁","createTime":"2020-03-03T13:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T13:32:25.000Z","uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b5070e53fcb11524e881ebde202d8f293c760726","tid":1908773,"uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"福建幫搵你班小股東幫手找數者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎持續，租戶紛要求減租，但優品360（2360）今日與主席林子峰有份持有、位於香港仔華貴坊的店舖續租3年，每月固定租金為31,500萬元，以及按每月總收入10%計超出固定基本租金的銷售租金，固定租金較上一份租約3萬月增近5%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200303&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60669214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200303%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60669214&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=2460f181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200303%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60669214&h=474b7986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200303&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60669214</a>"}]}